## Component Overview

### 1. Page Header Component
Usage: <%#= render 'admin_controllers/shared/page_header', ... %>

Parameters:
- title: Page title (required)
- subtitle: Page description (optional)
- icon: Bootstrap icon class (optional, default: 'bi-file-text')
- icon_color: Bootstrap color name (optional, default: 'primary')
- back_path: Path for back button (optional)
- back_text: Text for back button (optional, default: '戻る')
- breadcrumbs: Array of breadcrumb items (optional)
- actions: Array of action buttons (optional)

### 2. Status Badge Component  
Usage: <%#= render 'admin_controllers/shared/status_badge', ... %>

Parameters:
- status: Status value (required)
- text: Display text (optional, will use humanized status if not provided)
- type: Badge type ('status', 'level', 'priority', 'store_type', default: 'status')
- icon: Custom icon (optional)
- size: Badge size ('sm', 'md', 'lg', default: 'md')

### 3. Action Buttons Component
Usage: <%#= render 'admin_controllers/shared/action_buttons', ... %>

Parameters:
- buttons: Array of button configurations (required)
- size: Button size ('sm', 'md', 'lg', default: 'sm')
- layout: Layout type ('group', 'dropdown', 'individual', default: 'group')
- align: Alignment ('start', 'center', 'end', default: 'end')
- class: Additional CSS classes

